			<description><![CDATA[<p>
	Senior Interactive Producer<br />
	Overview:<br />
	Genuine Interactive, a leading Boston-based Digital Marketing Agency, is seeking a Senior Interactive Producer to join our team. The primary responsibilities for this position are scoping, managing and delivering interactive projects. Candidates will work with a Digital Account Manager to consult with clients and lead design, development, and flash teams on interactive communications projects. The Interactive Producer will also have the opportunity to participate in business development activities with both new and existing clients.<br />
	Key Responsibilities:<br />
	&bull; Participate and drive client and internal project kick off meetings<br />
	&bull; Analyze web traffic and site analytics<br />
	&bull; Analyze web sites from a competitive, usability and strategy perspective<br />
	&bull; Present analyses, recommendations and deliverables based on client objectives<br />
	&bull; Lead Creative Brainstorming sessions and generate ideas for client campaigns and web sites<br />
	&bull; Oversee the implementation of creative and technical solutions<br />
	&bull; Must have advanced understanding of web development technologies (CMS, Database, etc.) but not necessarily the ability to program<br />
	Required Qualifications:<br />
	&bull; Minimum of 2 to 4 years&#39; experience as an Interactive Producer or Digital Account Manager<br />
	&bull; Knowledge of how HTML, CSS and Flash work<br />
	&bull; Experience working with graphic designers and web developers<br />
	&bull; Demonstrated ability to lead project teams though concept development to completion of project deliverables<br />
	&bull; Experience developing and managing projects schedules and budgets<br />
	&bull; Experience with Microsoft Project and full Microsoft Office suite</p>
